[ProtecNVGoggles]
Description=A common skateboard headgear, the Pro-Tec "Half Cut" Helmet has been gaining popularity in military and law-enforcement agencies from around the world since the 90's due to it's light weight and ease to be modified. Although it offers less protection compared to the PASGT helmet, it's extremely light weight and bump protection makes it a popular choice for CQB scenarios. The "Half Cut" helmet provides protection from pistol hollow point rounds, smaller variants of buckshot and small caliber full metal jacket rounds, but does little to stop rifle caliber rounds, larger variants of buckshot out of long barrels or shotgun slugs. The PVS-7 Night Vision Goggles work by amplifying available light and allow the wearer to see in dark areas. Due to their lack of color and limited field of vision, the goggles can make it more difficult to distinguish friend from foe.
FriendlyName=Pro-Tec Helmet PVS-7
